divs: Sighting DetailsIt was near the Engolasters lake. First I think it was the moon or a globus, but after the object went N to NE and I could see some lights (I think they were but I am not sure at this point, maybe blue). The object first was stopping but then it began move slowly and at 15 mins aprox. its accelerations was very fast and dissapier. First I don't look the object seriously but when it began move I was very exciting, it was amazing.
